WEBVTT

1
00:39:24.120 --> 00:39:25.630 
嘟-嘟-嘟-嘟-嘟?
Tun-tun-tun-tun-tun?

2
00:39:27.350 --> 00:39:28.940 
哦 然后再这样...
Oh, and then it could go...

3
00:39:29.010 --> 00:39:31.890 
哒啦啦-哒啦啦-哒啦啦-哒啦啦 嘟?
Darala-dalala-dalala-dalala Whenk?

4
00:39:34.980 --> 00:39:36.670 
那在舞台上布满熊熊烈火如何?
And what if everything was on fire?

5
00:39:37.410 --> 00:39:39.390 
对 熊熊烈火!
Yes! Fire everywhere!

6
00:39:39.550 --> 00:39:40.900 
灵感井喷!
Inspired.

7
00:39:40.940 --> 00:39:43.760 
你是个天生的艺术家
You. You have the spirit of an artist.

8
00:39:45.730 --> 00:39:48.690 
舞者退场 音乐淡出 灯光关闭
The dancers exit. The music fades. The lights go out.

9
00:39:48.800 --> 00:39:51.940 
然后欧内斯托·德拉库斯升上舞台中央
And Ernesto de la Cruz rises to the stage.

